name: Sterling silver stacking ring set
description:
A beautiful sterling silver stacking ring set. 

Each ring in the set is different from the other to add a beautiful variety and detail in this set. One ring is made with silver beaded wire. Another ring is made of silver twisted wire. Finally, one ring is a plain round silver ring that I textured with my hammer for a great sparkle and shine! 

These rings will be custom made in your size

name: Sterling silver blue druzy necklace
description:
An amazing sterling silver titanium blue druzy pendant necklace.

This is a gorgeous 12 x 16 mm titanium blue oval grade AA druzy stone. I set it into a bezel setting with a gorgeous delicate design. This pendant comes with a 16 inch sterling silver chain. This druzy stone is absolutely stunning and eye-catching!

name: Gemstone silver stacking rings ruby citrine amethyst
description:
Gemstone stacking ring set with citrine, amethyst, and lab grown ruby sterling silver rings.

This set features one ring with a grade AAA 4 mm amethyst stone bezel set on a sterling silver band with a beaded pattern. I added a 4 mm bezel set lab grown ruby stone to a thick 2 mm plain sterling silver band. Finally there is a bezel set round 4 mm citrine stone on a thin sterling silver band. These colors are just amazing together!
 
These rings will be custom made in your size.

name: Sterling silver infinity ring sailors knot
description:
Sterling silver love knot ring, infinity ring, with a twisted rope pattern.

This ring is definitely a stunner! I started by making the intricate double knot pattern using a sterling silver wire with a twist pattern. The twist adds a great detail and style and looks like a little twisted rope! This ring looks great alone, but would also be great stacked with more of our sterling silver stack rings. 


I will custom make this ring in the size you specify.

name: Sterling silver hammered wide band ring
description:
A stunning sterling silver wide band ring with a hammered texture.

This is an amazing wide sterling silver band ring, and would be great for men or women. I took a thick sterling silver strip and soldered it into this beautiful ring. I then texture this ring with my hammer for a great organic look. The band is a 1/2-inch wide. This would be a great alternative wedding band, and is my new favorite!
 
This ring will be custom made in whatever size you specify.
